{"tid":1469364,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"前線賣命 唔係現場既有資格批評？","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:34:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T01:53:20.000Z","uid":32669,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a57bf4856a7567c7ef30b8ea1c5d52cb8237617b","tid":1469364,"uid":32669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:34:14.000Z","msg":"發過幾次夢， 好多時見到有現場有激烈討論。 其實討論好正常，因為我地係自發既。 唔該唔係現場既人唔好做賽後軍師，你連去都無去過現場，你仲好意思屌前線？ 人地扑心扑命打， 你自己自私返工 做自己野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：慚愧之人 818見"},{"pid":"b7bb1f9782647c14b5c820fb26b6bc12f1cfc121","tid":1469364,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:37:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14473199905108574b7df5416afe14c66bf81182","tid":1469364,"uid":247008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201